CMD: "take picture"

5
00:00:26,670 --> 00:00:31,670
Robot: "I see more than one wall.  Which wall should I go to?"

6
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:37,840
CMD: "go straight ahead"

7
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:49,650
Robot: "How far should I go straight ahead?"

8
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:50,290
CMD: "until you reach the wall"

9
00:00:47,990 --> 00:00:52,990
CMD: "then turn left ninety degrees"

10
00:00:51,390 --> 00:00:56,390
CMD: "send picture"

11
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:25,880
CMD: "until you reach the wall"

12
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:27,800
Robot: "I will go straight until I reach the wall closest to me, turn left 90 degrees and send a picture."

13
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:44,120
Robot: "sent"

